@startuml mxn-problem
!include ../../../config/_standard-style.puml

title M×N Integration Problem - Without MCP

rectangle "AI Applications (M=5)" #FFE5E5 {
  component "Claude" <<agent>> as A1
  component "ChatGPT" <<agent>> as A2
  component "Gemini" <<agent>> as A3
  component "GitHub Copilot" <<agent>> as A4
  component "Custom Agent" <<agent>> as A5
}

rectangle "Data Sources (N=10)" #E5F5FF {
  database "PostgreSQL" as D1
  database "Salesforce" as D2
  database "GitHub" as D3
  database "Google Drive" as D4
  database "Slack" as D5
  database "Jira" as D6
  database "MongoDB" as D7
  database "Redis" as D8
  database "S3" as D9
  database "Elasticsearch" as D10
}

note right of A1 : Each AI app needs\ncustom integration\nfor each data source

A1 ..> D1 : custom
A1 ..> D2 : custom
A1 ..> D3 : custom
A1 ..> D4 : custom
A1 ..> D5 : custom

A2 ..> D1 : custom
A2 ..> D2 : custom
A2 ..> D3 : custom
A2 ..> D4 : custom
A2 ..> D5 : custom

A3 ..> D1 : custom
A3 ..> D2 : custom
A3 ..> D3 : custom
A3 ..> D6 : custom
A3 ..> D7 : custom

A4 ..> D1 : custom
A4 ..> D2 : custom
A4 ..> D8 : custom
A4 ..> D9 : custom

A5 ..> D1 : custom
A5 ..> D10 : custom

note bottom : M × N = 5 × 10 = 50 custom integrations needed!\nEach with different APIs, auth methods, and data formats

@enduml